docs\context\architecture-brief.md:51:| FR-010 | `AC-010`、`AC-019`、`AC-020` | taskId/requestId 串联、阶段事件完整性 | `contracts/` 审计与事件契约，`tests/` 日志串联测试 |
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:52:| FR-011 | `AC-011`、`AC-E026` | 先失效再删除、可重试记录 | `contracts/` 清理作业契约，`tests/` 清理测试 |
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:53:| FR-012 | `AC-012`、`AC-E015` | 批次边界取消、FAILED 才可重试、禁止重复派发 | `contracts/` 取消/重试契约，`tests/` 状态机测试 |
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:54:| FR-013 | `AC-013`、`AC-014`、`AC-015`、`AC-016`、`AC-019` | attemptNo、幂等冲突、锁接管、配置快照 | `contracts/` 创建/快照契约，`tests/` 幂等和接管测试 |
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:55:| FR-014 | `AC-017`、`AC-018`、`AC-E022`、`AC-E023` | 样板字段、游标稳定性、压测、敏感字段脱敏 | `contracts/` 样板契约，`tests/` 样板与压测测试 |
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:134:1. 先 FR-001 / FR-013，确认创建、幂等、快照和锁链路。
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:135:2. 再 FR-008 / FR-009，确认集中查询、权限和脱敏。
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:136:3. 再 FR-006 / FR-003，确认分片打包、文件发布和下载保护。
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:137:4. 再 FR-005 / FR-011 / FR-012，确认调度、清理、取消与重试。
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:138:5. 最后 FR-014，确认采购订单样板可作为压测和回归证据。
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:172:| `task-api` | `contracts/openapi.yaml`、`contracts/api/` | `tests/contract/`、`tests/backend/` | `src/task-api/` | FR-001、FR-002、FR-003、FR-004、FR-012、FR-013 |
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:173:| `registry-config` | `contracts/api/`、`contracts/query/` | `tests/contract/`、`tests/backend/`、`tests/query/` | `src/registry-config/` | FR-007、FR-008、FR-013 |
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:174:| `scheduler` | `contracts/scheduler/` | `tests/scheduler/` | `src/scheduler/` | FR-005、FR-013 |
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:175:| `query-executor` | `contracts/query/` | `tests/query/` | `src/query-executor/` | FR-006、FR-008、FR-009、FR-014 |
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:176:| `file-service` | `contracts/file/` | `tests/file/` | `src/file-service/` | FR-003、FR-006、FR-011 |
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:177:| `cleanup-job` | `contracts/file/` | `tests/file/`、`tests/scheduler/` | `src/cleanup-job/` | FR-011 |
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:178:| `audit-log` | `contracts/audit/` | `tests/backend/`、`tests/contract/` | `src/audit-log/` | FR-010、FR-013 |
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:179:| `sample-purchase-order` | `contracts/sample/`、`contracts/query/` | `tests/sample/`、`tests/query/`、`tests/file/` | `src/sample-purchase-order/` | FR-014 |
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:222:执行阶段事件固定为 `QUERY_READY`、`QUERY_BATCH_DONE`、`FILE_PART_WRITTEN`、`PACKAGE_DONE`、`FILE_VERIFIED`、`DELIVERY_READY`。事件必须能通过 `taskId`、`attemptNo`、`requestId`、`queryTemplateVersion`、`datasourceCode` 和 `batchCheckpoint` 串联，作为 FR-010、FR-013 和 FR-014 的证据骨架。
plans\features\export-platform.dev-plan.md:21:| P4 | 实现 task-api 与 registry-config | 创建、查询、历史、下载、进度/详情、注册、启停、幂等 | P2/P3 | FR-001、FR-002、FR-004、FR-007、FR-013 |
plans\features\export-platform.dev-plan.md:22:| P5 | 实现 scheduler 与 query-executor | 抢锁、租约、游标、数据范围、批次事件 | P2/P3 | FR-005、FR-006、FR-008、FR-010 |
plans\features\export-platform.dev-plan.md:23:| P6 | 实现 file-service 与 cleanup-job | 临时对象、发布、过期清理、下载保护 | P2/P3 | FR-003、FR-011 |
plans\features\export-platform.dev-plan.md:24:| P7 | 实现 cancel/retry 和权限/脱敏 | 状态机、内部取消、权限和脱敏收口 | P2/P3 | FR-009、FR-012 |
plans\features\export-platform.dev-plan.md:25:| P8 | 实现采购订单样板 | 样板合同、边界数据、10 万行压测证据 | P2/P3/P4/P5/P6/P7 | FR-014 |
plans\features\export-platform.dev-plan.md:42:| T1 契约总入口 | P1 | 复核并扩展已存在的 `contracts/README.md`，再把 `contracts/openapi.yaml`、目录约定和 FR-001 / FR-003 / FR-005 / FR-008 / FR-013 / FR-014 的接口、状态、错误码定住 |
plans\features\export-platform.dev-plan.md:71:| DB 抢锁与租约 | `lockOwner + lockExpireAt + leaseRenewedAt`，时间以数据库时间为准，默认租约 5 分钟 | `contracts/scheduler/`、`tests/scheduler/`、`src/scheduler/` | FR-005 / FR-013 的抢锁、续租、接管测试 |
plans\features\export-platform.dev-plan.md:77:| 审计链路 | 动作审计 + 阶段事件必须能按 `taskId/attemptNo/requestId` 串联 | `contracts/audit/`、`tests/backend/`、`src/audit-log/` | FR-010 与所有失败态证据 |
plans\features\export-platform.dev-plan.md:94:- 任务 A：复核 `contracts/README.md` 并落 `contracts/openapi.yaml`，先固定 FR-001 至 FR-014 的接口、状态、错误码和样板契约，包含 FR-002 的查询进度/详情路径。
plans\features\export-platform.dev-plan.md:102:- 先验收 FR-001、FR-002、FR-013，确认任务创建、查询进度/详情、幂等、配置快照和锁租约。
plans\features\export-platform.dev-plan.md:103:- 再验收 FR-008、FR-009，确认查询契约、数据范围和脱敏。
plans\features\export-platform.dev-plan.md:104:- 再验收 FR-006、FR-003、FR-011，确认分片、文件发布和过期清理。
plans\features\export-platform.dev-plan.md:105:- 再验收 FR-012，确认取消和重试状态机。
plans\features\export-platform.dev-plan.md:106:- 最后验收 FR-014，确认采购订单样板可作为主样板和压测证据。
